  • Deprecated Interfaces 
    Interface and Description
    org.mozilla.geckoview.WebExtensionController.TabDelegate
    Use WebExtension.TabDelegate and WebExtension.SessionTabDelegate.
  • Deprecated Classes 
    Class and Description
    org.mozilla.geckoview.ContentBlockingController.ExceptionList
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    org.mozilla.geckoview.RuntimeTelemetry.getSnapshots(boolean)
    Use Glean instead. Planned removal in 79 (bug 1620656).
    org.mozilla.geckoview.WebExtensionController.getTabDelegate()
    Use WebExtension.getTabDelegate() and WebExtension.SessionController.getTabDelegate(org.mozilla.geckoview.WebExtension).
    org.mozilla.geckoview.GeckoRuntime.registerWebExtension(WebExtension)
    Use WebExtensionController.installBuiltIn(java.lang.String) instead. This method will be removed in GeckoView 81.
    org.mozilla.geckoview.ContentBlockingController.restoreExceptionList(ContentBlockingController.ExceptionList)
    org.mozilla.geckoview.WebExtensionController.setTabDelegate(WebExtensionController.TabDelegate)
    Use WebExtension.setTabDelegate(org.mozilla.geckoview.WebExtension.TabDelegate) and WebExtension.SessionController.setTabDelegate(org.mozilla.geckoview.WebExtension, org.mozilla.geckoview.WebExtension.SessionTabDelegate).
    org.mozilla.geckoview.GeckoRuntime.unregisterWebExtension(WebExtension)
    Use WebExtensionController.uninstall(org.mozilla.geckoview.WebExtension) instead. This method will be removed in GeckoView 81.
  • Deprecated Constructors 
    Constructor and Description
    org.mozilla.geckoview.WebExtension(String, String, long, WebExtensionController)
    Use the return value of WebExtensionController.installBuiltIn(java.lang.String) instead. This method will be removed in GeckoView 81.
    org.mozilla.geckoview.WebExtension(String, WebExtensionController)
    Use the return value of WebExtensionController.installBuiltIn(java.lang.String) instead. This method will be removed in GeckoView 81.
